tract  SOLICITATIONS All solicitations will be advertised at www eva virginia gov in accordance with Commonwealth of Virginia and VMI policies  TRAINING AND OUTREACH VMI will offer supplier diversity training for its employees  particularly procurement staff through resources such as VASCUPP  DMBE and DGS  Such training may include  Workshops Technical Assistance Executive level roundtables   Procurement Services Procurement Services Home Purchasing Tips Supplier Diversity Program Contracts   Current Solicitations Procurement Services Forms Procurement Services Staff SPCC Online Reconciliation Training VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu Virginia Military Institute   Supplier Diversity Program    Virginia Military Institute   Supplier Diversity Program                        skip to content VMI VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI Menu About About Us Administrative Offices Institute Report News  Photos  Videos VMI Archives Museums VMI Museum System The VMI Museum New Market Battlefield Stonewall Jackson House For Visitors Directions   Map Employment Parents   Family Conferences Chessie Nature Trail Bookstore Resources MyVMI Directories Friendly URLs Post View Health and Safety Computing Academics Areas of Study Majors   Minors Arts   Humanities Engineering Information   Social Sciences Life Sciences Natural Sciences ROTC Enrichment Institute Honors Program International Programs Service 